requestBody.title: Owner reviews consolidated calendar state API Trace

data.instruction: Using concrete API reads and persisted state checks, validate this requirement is satisfied: "Acceptance actor/timestamp trail". If not satisfied, record exact gap and failing entities/endpoints.
data.expectedResult: Evidence either confirms requirement coverage or captures a precise, reproducible gap.

data.instruction: Using agents tools, create a biz representing The Multi-Step Medical Procedure. Use name/slug derived from saga context.
data.expectedResult: Biz is created, owner is auto-added as member with owner role, and biz id is captured.

data.instruction: Create or login the owner account through Better Auth endpoints, then verify session context can call authenticated API routes.
data.expectedResult: Owner session exists and authenticated routes return success for this user.
